==========================================================
=        LPAIR MC events generator -- CDF version        =
==========================================================

To compile this code, first ensure that you have a working
copy of CERNLIB library on your workstation.

Then edit the makefile in the src/ directory to link the
shared objects to the LPAIR executable by setting the
CERNLIB_LOCATION environment variable

Finally compile the code using the common command "make"
in order to get an "mylpair.exe" executable.
